title: Grateful Dead Live at Boston Garden on 1993-09-25
description:
Set 1

Cold Rain & Snow, Wang Dang Doodle, Loser, It's All Over Now, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, Cassidy, Deal

Set 2

Foolish Heart, Box Of Rain-> Crazy Fingers-> Corinna-> Jam-> Drums-> Space-> The Wheel-> All Along The Watchtower-> Black Peter, Black Peter-> One More Saturday Night, E: I Fought The Law
